it's actually okay to be them.

00:02:35.520 --> 00:02:38.120
See most of us have been judging
ourselves our entire lives for

00:02:38.120 --> 00:02:40.360
everything we choose,
for everything we are.

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:42.000
