changing the world comes in.

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:05.500
What I'd like to see is a
world where we can all be us.

00:03:05.500 --> 00:03:08.640
We can be everything we are,
all of the greatness of us.

00:03:08.640 --> 00:03:11.920
Embrace everything about us
and not have to cut any of it off.

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:14.420
